metadata.name: Black Flag Ukrainian Hall #4
metadata.description:
Black Flag photographs by glen E. friedman made at the Ukrainian Cultural Center in Los Angeles December 10th 1982 during sound check. 

photographs from the book "what I see" the BLACK FLAG photographs of glen E. friedman 

colorization by the Internet Trouble Maker a.k.a. Sean Bonner

100% of the primary sale of this NFT will be donated to benefit Ukrainian humanitarian efforts.
